   <concept id="DFARS-213.106-1"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">213.106-1</ph> Soliciting competition.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Considerations</i>.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(2)(i) Include an evaluation factor regarding
supply chain risk (see subpart <xref href="SUBPART_239.73.dita#DFARS-SUBPART_239.73"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">239.73</xref>) when acquiring
information technology, whether as a service or as a supply, that
is a covered system, is a part of a covered system, or is in support
of a covered system, as defined in <ph xtrc="DFARxref" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="239.7301.dita#DFARS-239.7301"
                     base="DFARS-239.7301"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">239.7301</xref>
            </ph>.</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(ii) See <xref href="215.101-2-70.dita#DFARS-215.101-2-70"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">215.101-2-70</xref> for limitations
and prohibitions on the use of the lowest price technically acceptable
source selection process, which are applicable to simplified acquisitions.</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(iii) See <ph xtrc="DFARxref" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="217.7801.dita#DFARS-217.7801"
                     base="DFARS-217.7801"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">217.7801</xref>
            </ph> for the
prohibition on the use of reverse auctions for personal protective
equipment and aviation critical safety items.</p>
      </conbody>
